arts.ttl: KNVB Cup: Heracles down Utrecht to reach Semi-finals
arts.sum: Heracles Almelo are into the semi-finals of the KNVB Cup after a 2-0 victory over FC Utrecht. Utrecht went into the game with Sebastien Haller on the bench as Ron Jans decided to begin with David Min. By the time Haller appeared at half-time, Utrecht were 2-0 down and chasing the game. arts.ttl: FC Twente sign former Bayern Munich midfielder Taylor Booth from Utrecht
arts.sum: FC Twente have signed American attacking midfielder Taylor Booth (23) from Utrecht for 2 million euros.

arts.ttl: FC Twente set to sign USMNT winger Taylor Booth from Utrecht in €2m deal
arts.sum: According to ESPN, Utrecht forward Taylor Booth is on the verge of completing a permanent move to FC Twente. The 23-year-old United States international has already agreed a three-and-a-half-year deal…
